  "text": "For many research approaches in cloud computing, the proposal of the CloudSim API is sufficient, however, when it is necessary to incorporate the cloud computing client entity, the simulator does not have this component available. Few published works consider an approach that includes a greater focus on the perspective of the client [CITATION_1] .",
